557
00:39:24,470 --> 00:39:25,190
That's right.

558
00:39:26,190 --> 00:39:29,360
Quit pretending to be a righteous man.

559
00:39:33,280 --> 00:39:34,650
Registrar, this is bad!

560
00:39:35,230 --> 00:39:36,280
The Four Greats are here.

561
00:39:59,670 --> 00:40:01,870
Three of the Four Greats have come.

562
00:40:02,000 --> 00:40:04,120
Mr. Pan is in the soup.

563
00:40:04,180 --> 00:40:05,940
[Heyang Magistrate's Office]

564
00:40:18,160 --> 00:40:20,100
What a grand gesture
from Silver Rain Terrace.

565
00:40:20,600 --> 00:40:22,280
Are you setting an ambush

566
00:40:22,770 --> 00:40:24,610
even before the real show starts?

567
00:40:28,520 --> 00:40:31,040
You got the wrong idea, Mr. Pan.

568
00:40:31,840 --> 00:40:34,150
Gathering you and Silver Rain Terrace
in the same place

569
00:40:34,360 --> 00:40:36,910
is a rare sight in Heyang.

570
00:40:37,840 --> 00:40:39,600
Both of us are here for this rare sight.

571
00:40:39,670 --> 00:40:41,430
We won't interfere. Don't worry.

572
00:40:43,840 --> 00:40:45,040
Mr. Gu is right.

573
00:40:45,470 --> 00:40:46,430
Young Master Zhuo said

574
00:40:46,520 --> 00:40:48,800
