575
00:40:49,150 --> 00:40:50,360
I was curious

576
00:40:50,520 --> 00:40:51,600
what he would do to chuck you out.

577
00:40:51,910 --> 00:40:53,870
So I came here with this anticipation.

578
00:40:54,910 --> 00:40:57,390
